  "rule_text": "Spell out zero\u2013nine; use numerals for 10+ (number.format.ten_plus_numerals). Exceptions \u2014 always numerals: percentages, ages, ratios. Percentages use the % sign (number.percent.sign = %), e.g., 74%.",
